-- Canon to buy back $640 million worth of own shares
-- 
-- Mon Jun 4, 2012 2:10am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/06/04/us-canon-buyback-idUSBRE85305F20120604

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Canon Inc ( 7751.T ) said on Monday it plans to buy back up to 50 billion yen ($640 million) worth of its own shares, or 1.4 percent of its shares outstanding, between June 5 and July 27. ($1 = 78.1200 Japanese yen) 
 (Reporting by  Mayumi Negishi )